  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This observational study compares the influence of Ringer's Lactate solution and Ringer's
      Acetate solution on organ function scores following severe burn injury.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      In the early period following severe burn injury volume replacement with high amounts of
      crystalloids is necessary. In this study we compare the organ function scores of a historical
      patient group, treated with Ringer's Lactate solution, with an actual patient population,
      treated with Ringer's Acetate solution.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
